sets.detail:
192 Melee Attack is to hit as hard as possible 
 200 Speed is to be as fast as possible, with Nimble it outspeeds Nimble Phagenaut, without Nimble, it outspeeds Nimble Barbadger 
 104 HP is to make Health Amulet give 12 HP every turn 
 4 Energy = 273 Energy at level 50 for (3 Meteor Smashes + 3 Cerebral Slashes)
sets.author: Epicly Epic Gamer

sets.detail:
200 Melee Attack with Brawny is to hit as hard as possible 
 200 Speed is to be as fast as possible, with Boots it outspeeds Boots Phagenaut and below 
 20 Energy = 276 Energy at level 50 for (5 Meteor Smashes) 
 80 HP is leftovers and improves overall bulk 
 This set requires a teammate with the Ability Specialization (preferably Meditoad) to faint and for Cosmiore-U to copy it with Surrogate
sets.author: Epicly Epic Gamer
